<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style2.css">
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kumbh+Sans:wght@400;700&family=Rubik:wght@400;500;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Comments</title>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="reply-card">
        <img src="images/avatars/image-juliusomo.png" alt="">
        <form action="/reply" method="post">
            <textarea name="comment" id="replyed-comment">@user name, </textarea>
            <button>REPLY</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="basic-card">
            <div class="score">
                <div id="add" class="controller">+</div>
                <div id="score-value">12</div>
                <div id="minus" class="controller">â€“</div>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <img class="avatar" src="images/avatars/image-amyrobson.png" alt="">
                    <h5>amyrobson</h5>
                    <h6>1 month ago</h6>
                    <div class="reply">
                        <img src="images/icon-reply.svg" alt="">
                        Reply
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p>
                    Impressive! Though it seems the drag feature could be improved. But overall it looks incredible.
                    You've nailed the design and the responsiveness at various breakpoints works really well.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>



    </div>
    <script src="js/app.js"></script>
</body>

</html>